resourcecontainers | where type == 'microsoft.resources/subscriptions' {0} | project SubscriptionId = subscriptionId, DisplayName = name, SubscriptionPolicies = properties.subscriptionPolicies

resources {0} | where bag_has_key(tags, '{1}') | project id, subscriptionId, resourceGroup, type, kind, managedBy, sku, name, location, identity, zones, extendedLocation, plan, tags | sort by tolower(id) asc

resources {0} | where bag_has_kvp(tags, '{1}', '{2}') | project id, subscriptionId, resourceGroup, type, kind, managedBy, sku, name, location, identity, zones, extendedLocation, plan, tags | sort by tolower(id) asc

resources {0} | mvexpand tagsEx = tags | extend tagKey = tostring(bag_keys(tagsEx)[0]) | where tagKey startswith '{1}' | project id, subscriptionId, resourceGroup, type, kind, managedBy, sku, name, location, identity, zones, extendedLocation, plan, tags | summarize any(subscriptionId), any(resourceGroup), any(type), any(kind), any(managedBy), any(sku), any(name), any(location), any(identity), any(zones), any(extendedLocation), any(plan), any(tags) by ['id'] | project id, subscriptionId=any_subscriptionId, resourceGroup=any_resourceGroup, type=any_type, managedBy=any_managedBy, sku=any_sku, name=any_name, location=any_location, identity=any_identity, zones=any_zones, extendedLocation=any_extendedLocation, plan=any_plan, tags=any_tags, ['kind']=['any_kind'] | sort by tolower(id) asc

resourcecontainers | where subscriptionId == '{0}' | where isnotempty(tags) | project id, tags, subscriptionId | mvexpand kind=array tags | extend tagKey = tostring(tags[0]) | extend tagValue = tostring(tags[1]) | where tagKey !startswith 'hidden-' | union (resources | where subscriptionId == '{0}' | where isnotempty(tags) | project id, tags, subscriptionId | mvexpand kind=array tags | extend tagKey = tostring(tags[0]) | extend tagValue = tostring(tags[1]) | where tagKey !startswith 'hidden-') | distinct id, tagKey, tagValue, subscriptionId | project-away id | extend tagName = tagKey | summarize tagValueCount = count() by tagName, tagValue, subscriptionId | summarize tagValueCounts=make_bag(pack(tagValue, tagValueCount)), total=sum(tagValueCount) by tagName | mvexpand kind=array tagValueCounts | extend tagValue = tostring(tagValueCounts[0]) | extend tagValueCount = toint(tagValueCounts[1]) | project tagName, total, tagValue, tagValueCount | order by tagName asc

vars.DeploymentsGeo.$comment: This variable allows the Deployments team to adopt geographies which do not align to the standard ARM regional geographies list.
